casebody.data:
Hyde, Respondent, v. Bullock et al., Appellants. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 17, 1892.) Action by Walter L. Hyde against Thomas S. Bullock and another.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Ed. Russell, for appellants. A. B. Chalmers, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
